"{\"uid\": \"rte.ie-sport-paris-2024-2024-0718-1460569-paris-prepares-for-unique-olympics-opening-ceremony\", \"noun_phrases\": [{\"sentence\": \"Paris will begin its Olympics extravaganza with an unprecedented opening ceremony on the river Seine on 26 July.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 112, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 0, \"end\": 5, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.5178989529094528e-22, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"its Olympics extravaganza\", \"from\": 17, \"to\": 42}, {\"ngram\": \"an unprecedented opening ceremony\", \"from\": 48, \"to\": 81}, {\"ngram\": \"the river Seine\", \"from\": 85, \"to\": 100}, {\"ngram\": \"26 July\", \"from\": 104, \"to\": 111}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Here is what you need to know about the ceremony.\", \"from\": 114, \"to\": 163, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the ceremony\", \"from\": 150, \"to\": 162}]}, {\"sentence\": \"WHAT WILL WE SEE?\", \"from\": 165, \"to\": 182, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Organisers have promised a show like no other.\", \"from\": 184, \"to\": 230, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Organisers\", \"from\": 184, \"to\": 194}, {\"ngram\": \"a show\", \"from\": 209, \"to\": 215}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Unlike for previous Olympics, the Paris 2024 opening ceremony will not take place in a stadium.\", \"from\": 232, \"to\": 327, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 266, \"end\": 276, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 6.369580098880326e-22, \"text\": \"Paris 2024\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"previous Olympics\", \"from\": 243, \"to\": 260}, {\"ngram\": \"place\", \"from\": 308, \"to\": 313}, {\"ngram\": \"a stadium\", \"from\": 317, \"to\": 326}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Instead, dozens of boats will carry thousands of athletes and performers on a 6km route along the Seine.\", \"from\": 329, \"to\": 433, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 427, \"end\": 432, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.3805301869356872e-18, \"text\": \"Seine\", \"types\": [\"Q47521\", \"Q4022\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"dozens\", \"from\": 338, \"to\": 344}, {\"ngram\": \"boats\", \"from\": 348, \"to\": 353}, {\"ngram\": \"thousands\", \"from\": 365, \"to\": 374}, {\"ngram\": \"athletes\", \"from\": 378, \"to\": 386}, {\"ngram\": \"performers\", \"from\": 391, \"to\": 401}, {\"ngram\": \"a 6km route\", \"from\": 405, \"to\": 416}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Departing from the Austerlitz bridge, the parade will sail by Notre-Dame de Paris cathedral and arrive near the Eiffel Tower, after passing under bridges and gateways, including the Pont des Arts and Pont Neuf, and near many of the French capital's landmarks.\", \"from\": 435, \"to\": 694, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 454, \"end\": 464, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gare_d'Austerlitz\", \"score\": 0.9999999999849933, \"rank\": 1.5233544108294882e-11, \"text\": \"Austerlitz\", \"types\": [\"Q719456\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gare_d'Austerlitz\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gare_d'Austerlitz\"}, {\"begin\": 617, \"end\": 630, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pont_des_Arts\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Pont des Arts\", \"types\": [\"Q12280\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pont_des_Arts\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pont_des_Arts\"}, {\"begin\": 635, \"end\": 644, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pont_Neuf\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.582098068080508e-47, \"text\": \"Pont Neuf\", \"types\": [\"Q12280\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pont_Neuf\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pont_Neuf\"}, {\"begin\": 667, \"end\": 673, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.9997044287783174, \"rank\": 0.00019652167016995687, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the parade\", \"from\": 473, \"to\": 483}, {\"ngram\": \"Notre-Dame de Paris cathedral\", \"from\": 497, \"to\": 526}, {\"ngram\": \"the Eiffel Tower\", \"from\": 543, \"to\": 559}, {\"ngram\": \"bridges\", \"from\": 581, \"to\": 588}, {\"ngram\": \"gateways\", \"from\": 593, \"to\": 601}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Organisers have said they will take advantage of the historic monuments, the riverbanks, the sky and water \\\"and there will not be a single riverbank or bridge that will not be filled with music, dance, or performance.\\\"\", \"from\": 698, \"to\": 916, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Organisers\", \"from\": 698, \"to\": 708}, {\"ngram\": \"advantage\", \"from\": 734, \"to\": 743}, {\"ngram\": \"the historic monuments\", \"from\": 747, \"to\": 769}, {\"ngram\": \"the riverbanks\", \"from\": 771, \"to\": 785}, {\"ngram\": \"the sky\", \"from\": 787, \"to\": 794}, {\"ngram\": \"water\", \"from\": 799, \"to\": 804}, {\"ngram\": \"a single riverbank\", \"from\": 828, \"to\": 846}, {\"ngram\": \"bridge\", \"from\": 850, \"to\": 856}, {\"ngram\": \"music\", \"from\": 886, \"to\": 891}, {\"ngram\": \"dance\", \"from\": 893, \"to\": 898}, {\"ngram\": \"performance\", \"from\": 903, \"to\": 914}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The show will have 12 parts, some of which will play on clich\\u00e9s about France.\", \"from\": 917, \"to\": 994, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 987, \"end\": 993, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.9999997783761746, \"rank\": 1.583824432296718e-07, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The show\", \"from\": 917, \"to\": 925}, {\"ngram\": \"12 parts\", \"from\": 936, \"to\": 944}, {\"ngram\": \"clich\\u00e9s\", \"from\": 973, \"to\": 980}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Athletes and artists will take part in the parade together.\", \"from\": 996, \"to\": 1055, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Athletes\", \"from\": 996, \"to\": 1004}, {\"ngram\": \"artists\", \"from\": 1009, \"to\": 1016}, {\"ngram\": \"part\", \"from\": 1027, \"to\": 1031}, {\"ngram\": \"the parade\", \"from\": 1035, \"to\": 1045}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Everything will be woven together, including the protocol (the speeches, the opening by the head of state, the anthems, etc.\", \"from\": 1057, \"to\": 1182, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Everything\", \"from\": 1058, \"to\": 1068}, {\"ngram\": \"the protocol\", \"from\": 1103, \"to\": 1115}, {\"ngram\": \"(the speeches\", \"from\": 1116, \"to\": 1129}, {\"ngram\": \"the opening\", \"from\": 1131, \"to\": 1142}, {\"ngram\": \"the head\", \"from\": 1146, \"to\": 1154}, {\"ngram\": \"state\", \"from\": 1158, \"to\": 1163}, {\"ngram\": \"the anthems\", \"from\": 1165, \"to\": 1176}]}, {\"sentence\": \"),\\\" organisers Thomas Jolly et Damien Gabriac told Le Monde newspaper.\", \"from\": 1182, \"to\": 1252, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1197, \"end\": 1203, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Thomas_Wayne\", \"score\": 0.8451814586049451, \"rank\": 0.1379144269556726, \"text\": \"Thomas\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Thomas_Wayne\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Thomas_Wayne\"}, {\"begin\": 1220, \"end\": 1227, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gabriac,_Aveyron\", \"score\": 0.8010054874943173, \"rank\": 0.1249999999999922, \"text\": \"Gabriac\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gabriac,_Aveyron\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gabriac,_Aveyron\"}, {\"begin\": 1233, \"end\": 1241, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Le_Monde\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Le Monde\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q234460\", \"Q11032\", \"Q1092563\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Le_Monde\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Le_Monde\"}], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The ceremony is due to start at 5.30pm Irish time and last about four hours.\", \"from\": 1254, \"to\": 1330, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1293, \"end\": 1303, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Time_in_the_Republic_of_Ireland\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Irish time\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Time_in_the_Republic_of_Ireland\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Time_in_the_Republic_of_Ireland\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The ceremony\", \"from\": 1254, \"to\": 1266}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Organisers said it would reach a climax at around 9.35 pm when the sun sets.\", \"from\": 1331, \"to\": 1407, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Organisers\", \"from\": 1331, \"to\": 1341}, {\"ngram\": \"a climax\", \"from\": 1362, \"to\": 1370}, {\"ngram\": \"around 9.35 pm\", \"from\": 1374, \"to\": 1388}]}, {\"sentence\": \"WHO WILL BE THERE?\", \"from\": 1409, \"to\": 1427, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The show will be attended by over 100 heads of state and government and over 300,000 spectators will watch from the river's banks, organisers said, adding that there will be some 80 giant screens along the way.\", \"from\": 1429, \"to\": 1639, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The show\", \"from\": 1429, \"to\": 1437}, {\"ngram\": \"over 100 heads\", \"from\": 1458, \"to\": 1472}, {\"ngram\": \"state\", \"from\": 1476, \"to\": 1481}, {\"ngram\": \"government\", \"from\": 1486, \"to\": 1496}, {\"ngram\": \"over 300,000 spectators\", \"from\": 1501, \"to\": 1524}, {\"ngram\": \"the river's banks\", \"from\": 1541, \"to\": 1558}, {\"ngram\": \"organisers\", \"from\": 1560, \"to\": 1570}, {\"ngram\": \"some 80 giant screens\", \"from\": 1603, \"to\": 1624}, {\"ngram\": \"the way\", \"from\": 1631, \"to\": 1638}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Paris 2024 committee said there would be about 10,500 athletes and some 222,000 people will get free invites, while 104,000 will have to buy a ticket.\", \"from\": 1641, \"to\": 1795, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1645, \"end\": 1655, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 6.369580098880326e-22, \"text\": \"Paris 2024\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"about 10,500 athletes\", \"from\": 1686, \"to\": 1707}, {\"ngram\": \"some 222,000 people\", \"from\": 1712, \"to\": 1731}, {\"ngram\": \"free invites\", \"from\": 1741, \"to\": 1753}, {\"ngram\": \"a ticket\", \"from\": 1786, \"to\": 1794}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Boats carrying the athletes will be equipped with cameras to allow those watching on TV or their phone to get a close-up view, the committee said.\", \"from\": 1799, \"to\": 1945, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Boats\", \"from\": 1799, \"to\": 1804}, {\"ngram\": \"the athletes\", \"from\": 1814, \"to\": 1826}, {\"ngram\": \"cameras\", \"from\": 1849, \"to\": 1856}, {\"ngram\": \"TV\", \"from\": 1884, \"to\": 1886}, {\"ngram\": \"their phone\", \"from\": 1890, \"to\": 1901}, {\"ngram\": \"a close-up view\", \"from\": 1909, \"to\": 1924}, {\"ngram\": \"the committee\", \"from\": 1926, \"to\": 1939}]}, {\"sentence\": \"There have been training sessions, and boats will be stored in a warehouse for a week before the opening ceremony for security reasons.\", \"from\": 1947, \"to\": 2082, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"training sessions\", \"from\": 1963, \"to\": 1980}, {\"ngram\": \"boats\", \"from\": 1986, \"to\": 1991}, {\"ngram\": \"a warehouse\", \"from\": 2010, \"to\": 2021}, {\"ngram\": \"a week\", \"from\": 2026, \"to\": 2032}, {\"ngram\": \"the opening ceremony\", \"from\": 2040, \"to\": 2060}, {\"ngram\": \"security reasons\", \"from\": 2065, \"to\": 2081}]}, {\"sentence\": \"WHAT ABOUT SECURITY?\", \"from\": 2084, \"to\": 2104, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"SECURITY\", \"from\": 2095, \"to\": 2103}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Organising the ceremony in the heart of an iconic city like Paris may make for great pictures, but it's also a major security challenge.\", \"from\": 2106, \"to\": 2242, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2166, \"end\": 2171, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.5178989529094528e-22, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the ceremony\", \"from\": 2117, \"to\": 2129}, {\"ngram\": \"the heart\", \"from\": 2133, \"to\": 2142}, {\"ngram\": \"an iconic city\", \"from\": 2146, \"to\": 2160}, {\"ngram\": \"great pictures\", \"from\": 2185, \"to\": 2199}, {\"ngram\": \"a major security challenge\", \"from\": 2215, \"to\": 2241}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Some 45,000 police will be dispatched to ensure the ceremony's security, including special intervention forces.\", \"from\": 2244, \"to\": 2355, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Some 45,000 police\", \"from\": 2244, \"to\": 2262}, {\"ngram\": \"the ceremony's security\", \"from\": 2292, \"to\": 2315}, {\"ngram\": \"special intervention forces\", \"from\": 2327, \"to\": 2354}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Snipers will be deployed on the top of buildings along the route.\", \"from\": 2356, \"to\": 2421, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Snipers\", \"from\": 2356, \"to\": 2363}, {\"ngram\": \"the top\", \"from\": 2384, \"to\": 2391}, {\"ngram\": \"buildings\", \"from\": 2395, \"to\": 2404}, {\"ngram\": \"the route\", \"from\": 2411, \"to\": 2420}]}, {\"sentence\": \"An anti-drone system will be in place.\", \"from\": 2422, \"to\": 2460, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"An anti-drone system\", \"from\": 2422, \"to\": 2442}, {\"ngram\": \"place\", \"from\": 2454, \"to\": 2459}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Spectators and local residents alike will need to carry permits on a QR code to get anywhere near the riverbanks from 18 July.\", \"from\": 2462, \"to\": 2588, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Spectators\", \"from\": 2462, \"to\": 2472}, {\"ngram\": \"local residents\", \"from\": 2477, \"to\": 2492}, {\"ngram\": \"permits\", \"from\": 2518, \"to\": 2525}, {\"ngram\": \"a QR code\", \"from\": 2529, \"to\": 2538}, {\"ngram\": \"the riverbanks\", \"from\": 2560, \"to\": 2574}, {\"ngram\": \"18 July\", \"from\": 2580, \"to\": 2587}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Cars will not be allowed into the area, with few exceptions.\", \"from\": 2589, \"to\": 2649, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Cars\", \"from\": 2589, \"to\": 2593}, {\"ngram\": \"the area\", \"from\": 2619, \"to\": 2627}, {\"ngram\": \"few exceptions\", \"from\": 2634, \"to\": 2648}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Nearby metro stations will be closed, as will many of the bridges.\", \"from\": 2650, \"to\": 2716, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"metro stations\", \"from\": 2657, \"to\": 2671}, {\"ngram\": \"the bridges\", \"from\": 2704, \"to\": 2715}]}, {\"sentence\": \"No planes will be allowed to fly over Paris - unless they are part of the ceremony.\", \"from\": 2720, \"to\": 2803, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2758, \"end\": 2763, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.5178989529094528e-22, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"No planes\", \"from\": 2720, \"to\": 2729}, {\"ngram\": \"part\", \"from\": 2782, \"to\": 2786}, {\"ngram\": \"the ceremony\", \"from\": 2790, \"to\": 2802}]}, {\"sentence\": \"With wars in Gaza and Ukraine, and security concerns at home, France already has its security alert at its highest level.\", \"from\": 2805, \"to\": 2926, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2818, \"end\": 2822, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gaza_Strip\", \"score\": 0.967023037629225, \"rank\": 0.03410152714835787, \"text\": \"Gaza\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gaza_Strip\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gaza_Strip\"}, {\"begin\": 2827, \"end\": 2834, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ukraine\", \"score\": 0.999998203251175, \"rank\": 1.6279953621460577e-06, \"text\": \"Ukraine\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ukraine\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ukraine\"}, {\"begin\": 2867, \"end\": 2873, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.9999997783761746, \"rank\": 1.583824432296718e-07, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"wars\", \"from\": 2810, \"to\": 2814}, {\"ngram\": \"security concerns\", \"from\": 2840, \"to\": 2857}, {\"ngram\": \"home\", \"from\": 2861, \"to\": 2865}, {\"ngram\": \"its security alert\", \"from\": 2886, \"to\": 2904}, {\"ngram\": \"its highest level\", \"from\": 2908, \"to\": 2925}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Officials have said there were no specific terror threats to the 26 July ceremony.\", \"from\": 2928, \"to\": 3010, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Officials\", \"from\": 2928, \"to\": 2937}, {\"ngram\": \"no specific terror threats\", \"from\": 2959, \"to\": 2985}, {\"ngram\": \"the 26 July ceremony\", \"from\": 2989, \"to\": 3009}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But should specific concerns arise, there are back-up plans, that would either see the ceremony limited to the Trocadero square near the Eiffel tower, or the Stade de France stadium.\", \"from\": 3012, \"to\": 3194, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3170, \"end\": 3185, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stade_de_France\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Stade de France\", \"types\": [\"Q41176\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stade_de_France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stade_de_France\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"should specific concerns\", \"from\": 3016, \"to\": 3040}, {\"ngram\": \"back-up plans\", \"from\": 3058, \"to\": 3071}, {\"ngram\": \"the ceremony\", \"from\": 3095, \"to\": 3107}, {\"ngram\": \"the Trocadero square\", \"from\": 3119, \"to\": 3139}, {\"ngram\": \"the Eiffel tower\", \"from\": 3145, \"to\": 3161}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The main potential risk would be from a lone attacker, officials have said over the past months, while also flagging potential petty crime and possible protests, from environmental activists, the far right and far left, the pro-Palestinian movement or others.\", \"from\": 3198, \"to\": 3457, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The main potential risk\", \"from\": 3198, \"to\": 3221}, {\"ngram\": \"a lone attacker\", \"from\": 3236, \"to\": 3251}, {\"ngram\": \"officials\", \"from\": 3253, \"to\": 3262}, {\"ngram\": \"the past months\", \"from\": 3278, \"to\": 3293}, {\"ngram\": \"potential petty crime\", \"from\": 3315, \"to\": 3336}, {\"ngram\": \"possible protests\", \"from\": 3341, \"to\": 3358}, {\"ngram\": \"environmental activists\", \"from\": 3365, \"to\": 3388}]}, {\"sentence\": \"A man was arrested in May in Saint-Etienne, suspected of planning an attack in the name of Islamic State at the city's soccer stadium during the Olympics.\", \"from\": 3459, \"to\": 3613